      ],
      "message": "test: add addnode connection limit test to rpc_net.py\n\nAdd test_addnode_connection_limit to NetTest in rpc_net.py.\nThe test restarts node 0 with -maxconnections=0 to verify that\naddnode connections bypass the general connection limit and are\nindependently capped at MAX_ADDNODE_CONNECTIONS (8).\n\nNodes 2-10 serve as addnode targets (9 targets, only 8 can\nconnect). The test verifies the cap is enforced, then removes\none peer and confirms the previously-blocked node takes the\nfreed slot.\n\nAddresses https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/28635",
      "committer": {
        "name": "Andrew Barnes",
        "email": "andrew.jaguars@gmail.com",
        "date": "2026-03-16T20:07:43Z"
